data.description: Just like new! Take a look at this beautiful split level with WALK-OUT basement. This newly built home offers quality features including vinyl plank floors, stainless appliances, tile backsplash and granite c-tops. You'll love the full cathedral ceiling throughout this open concept home. Oversized owner's suite complete with private bathroom and large W.I.C. Energy star certified with money saving features including high-efficient Carrier furnace, A/C, and double pane windows. Lower level can be enclosed for a 4th bedroom. You'll love this beautiful quiet community just minutes from South Have and Lake Michigan. Owner selling due to Military relocation. Schedule your tour today!
